{
  "description": "A hummingbird is captured mid-flight, appearing to drink nectar from a vibrant, dark red flower spike. The flower emerges from a dark, almost black stem with numerous blooms clustered at the top. The background is a lush, out-of-focus green consisting of fern-like foliage, creating a bokeh effect. Some orange and yellow flowers are visible softly in the very background, adding a subtle contrast. The hummingbird is small and delicate, with blurred wings suggesting rapid movement. The lighting is soft and diffused, creating a natural, vibrant aesthetic.",
